%section.tbs-section
  %h1.page-header#navs Navs
  %p.lead
    Navs available in Bootstrap have shared markup,
    starting with the base
    %code .nav
    class, as well as shared states.
    Swap modifier classes to switch between each style.

  %h3#navs-flaps Flaps
  %p
    Flaps are intended for use as top-level navigation items.
    Note the
    %code .nav-flaps
    class requires the
    %code .nav
    base class.

  .tbs-example
    %ul.nav.nav-flaps
      %li.active
        %a{href: '#'} Home
      %li
        %a{href: '#'} Profile
      %li
        %a{href: '#'} Messages
  .highlight
    :markdown
          %ul.nav.nav-flaps
            %li.active
              %a{href: '#'} Home
            %li
              %a{href: '#'} Profile
            %li
              %a{href: '#'} Messages
